00:10:29.440 --> 00:10:30.550
them.

00:10:30.560 --> 00:10:32.390
You're sitting here.

00:10:32.400 --> 00:10:35.310
You tell them.

00:10:35.320 --> 00:10:37.430
I ain't going to steal her thunder.

00:10:37.440 --> 00:10:38.310
Here,

00:10:38.320 --> 00:10:41.110
you can sit on my lap.

