have

00:10:42.829 --> 00:10:42.839
to—you

00:10:42.839 --> 00:10:45.230
told it really good. I know.

00:10:45.240 --> 00:10:47.790
Can you see her?

00:10:47.800 --> 00:10:49.190
All right. Tell them.

