00:11:01.480 --> 00:11:03.670
here to my elbow. And it traveled. It

00:11:03.680 --> 00:11:05.230
kind of stopped right there,

00:11:05.240 --> 00:11:06.950
but it was all through my hand. And I

00:11:06.960 --> 00:11:08.630
just felt it vibrating like a

00:11:08.640 --> 00:11:10.070
vibration,

00:11:10.080 --> 00:11:12.350
like a current. And I was

00:11:12.360 --> 00:11:14.270
