00:11:14.280 --> 00:11:15.950
praying and I was feeling

00:11:15.950 --> 00:11:15.960
it—and

00:11:15.960 --> 00:11:17.950
I was thinking, 'Wow, this is like my

00:11:17.960 --> 00:11:19.950
hand. I can feel the power of God.'And I

00:11:19.960 --> 00:11:22.030
was just weeping.

00:11:22.040 --> 00:11:24.190
And then she put her hand up here on my

00:11:24.200 --> 00:11:26.430
