00:11:26.440 --> 00:11:28.310
down my arm clear to my elbow, and it

00:11:28.320 --> 00:11:30.070
went all the way up and down.

00:11:30.080 --> 00:11:32.750
My whole hand was just

00:11:32.760 --> 00:11:34.470
under the power for

00:11:34.480 --> 00:11:36.950
over an hour. It was like being electrocuted.

00:11:36.960 --> 00:11:39.550
Yes. And it really was amazing

00:11:39.560 --> 00:11:41.750
because I've never seen you do that. And

00:11:41.760 --> 00:11:44.350
even our littlest was like, 'Daddy, can

00:11:44.360 --> 00:11:46.630
Mommy control her

00:11:46.630 --> 00:11:46.640
hand?'Because

00:11:46.640 --> 00:11:48.110
